{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a older man, by the name of Fakturovskii.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a young man who was actually from Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he came as a refugee, and he was taken in to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we were actually five.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We decided that, before anything, we would explore the-- get to this house where we had the supplies, and we will explore through this-- in the second floor, and we used the 13-year-old boy.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, he was our lookout to see in time when the guard is-- how often the guard is moving.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had also wire cutters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was a dark night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Not stars or the moon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we waited three or four days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were still there in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We run out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And, for some reason, the guards, when they counted the people, they were-- they were not-- truthfully, they were not as strict as like six or seven or eight months ago.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They already became concerned with their own fate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They thought that-- they-- they thought a little bit more about their own fate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The matter of Jews became already secondary in a certain way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we timed the guards' time, and we cut out-- in the middle of the night, when it was quite dark, and the guard was making his run, we just cut through the fence, and we run to the next closest neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In order to-- because nighttime, we wouldn't be able to go too far, because they would spot us right away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw already-- also, previously, there were many ambulances and many wounded German soldiers who were brought from the front to Lithuania too, and there were taken to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, we slept over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
